Package com.beemediate.beemediate.infrastructure.odoo.mapper

Class OrderMapper

java.lang.Object
com.beemediate.beemediate.infrastructure.odoo.mapper.OrderMapper
public final class OrderMapper extends Object
Classe utility per mappare i dati ricevuti da Odoo in un OrderStructure. A tale scopo, la classe si serve delle classi "DTO" presenti in com.beemediate.beemediate.infrastructure.odoo.dto.
